  <entry>
    <title>整一个铅酸电池欠压保护板</title>
    <url>/2024/06/01/ele-diy1/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><del>咕了N个月没发博客了，出来诈下尸</del><br>前段时间买了一个 12V 9AH 的铅酸电池，用来当大功率电源用。使用时可能会遇到电池过放或短路，这时保护板就可以及时断电，避免电池或电路受到更大的损伤。这个保护板参照了这篇文章来制作：<a href="https://www.eet-china.com/news/202107011132.html">https://www.eet-china.com/news/202107011132.html</a></p>
<p>贴上电路：<img src="https://blog.haf208.cc/cusimg/extra/ele-diy1/circurt.webp"></p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center">制作所用原件</th>
<th align="center">型号 (或参数)</th>
<th align="center">数量</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center">MOS 管</td>
<td align="center">NCEP40PT15D</td>
<td align="center">3</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">三级管</td>
<td align="center">S8050 &#x2F; S8550</td>
<td align="center">1</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">电压基准芯片</td>
<td align="center">TL431</td>
<td align="center">1</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">电阻</td>
<td align="center">10Ω, 100Ω, 330Ω, 1kΩ, 6.8kΩ, 10kΩ</td>
<td align="center">10kΩ x2, 其余都是x1</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">电容</td>
<td align="center">0603 10nF</td>
<td align="center">1</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">其他</td>
<td align="center">undefined</td>
<td align="center">undefined</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>板子到手才发现，当初在凌晨画的板子画错了，又是飞线伺候（哭笑）<br><img src="https://blog.haf208.cc/cusimg/extra/ele-diy1/01.webp"><br><img src="https://blog.haf208.cc/cusimg/extra/ele-diy1/02.webp"><br><img src="https://blog.haf208.cc/cusimg/extra/ele-diy1/03.webp"></p>
]]></content>
